EUROPEAN LOCAL FIBRE ALLIANCE (ELFA) is a new shared voice from alternative public and private local fibre operators calling for a more ambitious European Digital agenda and the acceleration of fibre deployment in Europe to power ultrafast broadband to citizens and businesses.&#xd;
